dct_title_s: Riparian map of property lines in Ridgefield and Englewood Townships along the Hudson River
dct_description_sm: Map indicating personal property riparian lines of Ridgefield and Englewood Township along the Hudson River
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
There are dates annotated in certain properties of the year 1874; map date is inferred from that year.
